; under rocks and in rock crevices (
<bibRefCitation author="Haig, J." box="[1238,1361,1462,1488]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" pagination="1 - 440" refId="ref72816" refString="Haig, J. (1960) The Porcellanidae (Crustacea: Anomura) of the Eastern Pacific. Allan Hancock Pacific Expedition, 24, 1 - 440." type="journal article" year="1960">Haig 1960</bibRefCitation>
