<bibRefCitation author="Gore, R. H." box="[151,273,1498,1524]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" pagination="1 - 34" refId="ref72204" refString="Gore, R. H. (1982) Porcellanid crabs from the coasts of Mexico and Central America (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura). Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology, 363, 1 - 34. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00810282.363" type="journal article" year="1982">Gore 1982</bibRefCitation>
